02:09:40.820 --> 02:09:46.170
thrust spear and blade towards his illusory body,
arrows and spells passing through harmlessly and

02:09:46.170 --> 02:09:49.972
clattering, and splashing, exploding against
distant pillars across the room.

02:09:49.972 --> 02:10:00.728
The smoke subsides and he stands there untouched.
"Quite the tea party you've gathered here, Vord. I

02:10:00.728 --> 02:10:11.527
"suppose celebration is in order. After all, you
