02:10:11.527 --> 02:10:20.513
"you that I'm quite excited about. Don't rush the
surprise, friends. I'll bring it to you; do not

02:10:20.513 --> 02:10:30.489
"fret. You're all gathered here in one place. It
would be a perfect place for an ambush, wouldn't

02:10:30.489 --> 02:10:41.247
"you say? But where's the fun in that, when there
are so many less-protected loved ones to send my

02:10:41.247 --> 02:10:45.577
"shadows to?

