02:14:17.650 --> 02:14:22.321
of the city, and some to make their way northward
to wherever Thar Amphala will be found, head on.

02:14:22.321 --> 02:14:26.718
While this happens, and you're currently attuning
to this ring--

02:14:26.718 --> 02:14:31.077
