02:28:44.764 --> 02:28:47.771
the last time we are fucked right out of the
gate.

02:28:47.771 --> 02:28:55.572
MATT: "What do you perceive as the weaknesses you
suffered in that previous battle?"

02:28:55.572 --> 02:28:57.924
LIAM: What was that?

02:28:57.924 --> 02:29:02.445
MATT: "What do you perceive are the weaknesses
that you suffered in that previous battle?"

02:29:02.445 --> 02:29:04.313
LIAM: He was able to hold us, magically.

02:29:04.313 --> 02:29:11.706
MATT: "There are ways to make sure those bindings
