02:33:52.224 --> 02:34:08.859
"good use." And she glances off to the side of your
pouch, closed as it is. "Come back." She turns

02:34:08.859 --> 02:34:11.339
around to go and join Kima.

02:34:11.339 --> 02:34:14.932
